tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE team_collaboration_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_id INT,
    employee_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE EmployeeFeedback (
	feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	emp_id INT,
	team_id INT,
	feedback_text TEXT,
	feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Employee (
	emp_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	emp_name VARCHAR(50),
	email VARCHAR(50),
	phone_number VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE Team (
	team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	team_name VARCHAR(50),
	team_leader_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE CollaborationRating (
	rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	feedback_id INT,
	communication_rating INT,
	cooperation_rating INT
)
